# Using SiMoN

[hfst-tools-list]: https://kitwiki.csc.fi/twiki/bin/view/KitWiki/HfstCommandLineTools

The binaries of SiMoN can be opened with the various tools of the HFST-Suite to perform morphological analysis for the Sicilian/Italian language on a word basis.
Below you can find some explanatory usage examples. A full list of available HFST tools can be found on the [respective HFST wiki page][hfst-tools-list].

